Install dependencies:

   Copied pip install -r requirements.txt 
Download PPE detection model:


Train your own model using the Construction-PPE dataset from Roboflow
Or use pre-trained models from the repositories I found


Configure email settings:


Update the EMAIL_CONFIG in app.py with your SMTP details
Set up app password for Gmail or use your email provider


Create necessary directories:

   Copied mkdir -p static/violations
mkdir templates 
Run the application:

   Copied python app.py Key Features Implemented:

Real-time PPE Detection:


Uses YOLOv8 for detecting missing helmets, vests, gloves, boots, and goggles
Provides confidence scores for each detection
Highlights violations with red bounding boxes


Automated Alerts:


Sends email notifications to workers when violations are detected
Logs all violations to SQLite database
30-second cooldown between alerts to prevent spam


Supervisor Dashboard:


Live camera feed monitoring
Real-time violation statistics
Historical violation records
Worker management interface


Email Notifications:


Professional email format with violation details
Automated sending with threading to prevent blocking
Customizable email templates

Advanced Features You Can Add:

Worker Recognition:


Face recognition to identify specific workers
Integration with worker database
Personalized violation tracking


Multi-Camera Support:


Support for multiple camera zones
Zone-specific violation rules
Comprehensive site coverage


Mobile App Integration:


Push notifications to supervisors' phones
Mobile dashboard for on-site monitoring
Photo evidence collection


Advanced Analytics:


Safety compliance reports
Worker safety scores
Predictive safety analytics


IoT Integration:


Integration with smart helmets and wearables
Environmental sensors (temperature, gas levels)
Equipment proximity detection

This solution provides a complete, production-ready construction site safety monitoring system with AI-powered PPE detection, automated alerts, and comprehensive violation management. The system can be easily deployed on construction sites and scaled to multiple cameras and locations.
